videos.headline: Hendon Hooker finds Cedric Tillman for leaping TD grab for Tennessee
videos.description: Tennessee QB Hendon Hooker connects with Cedric Tillman on a 41-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hendon Hooker finds Cedric Tillman for leaping TD grab for Tennessee) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue responds with quick 75-yard TD
videos.description: Purdue QB Aidan O'Connell finds Broc Thompson for a 75-yard touchdown as the Boilermakers tie the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdue responds with quick 75-yard TD) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue's fumble recovery leads to Payne Durham TD catch
videos.description: Purdue recovers a fumble late in the first half, then makes Tennessee pay with a short touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdue's fumble recovery leads to Payne Durham TD catch) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hendon Hooker passes to Velus Jones Jr. for 15-yard Tennessee TD
videos.description: Hendon Hooker passes to Velus Jones Jr. who follows a block up the sideline to score a 15-yard touchdown for Tennessee early in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hendon Hooker passes to Velus Jones Jr. for 15-yard Tennessee TD) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue retakes the lead on unreal corner TD
videos.description: Aidan O'Connell throws a perfect pass to TJ Sheffield who hauls it in in the corner of the end zone to make an unreal contested 10-yard touchdown catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdue retakes the lead on unreal corner TD) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Payne Durham escapes for unbelievable 62-yard Purdue TD
videos.description: Payne Durham makes the catch and appears to be stopped, but surprises everyone as he breaks free of a crowd of defenders and escapes down the sideline to score a 62-yard touchdown for Purdue.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Payne Durham escapes for unbelievable 62-yard Purdue TD) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Broc Thompson schools a defender for 70-yard Purdue TD
videos.description: Broc Thompson makes the sweet catch over a defender and takes off down the sideline to score an electric 70-yard Purdue touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Broc Thompson schools a defender for 70-yard Purdue TD) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalin Hyatt makes the grab for the tying TD
videos.description: Hendon Hooker fires a pass to Jalin Hyatt who makes the difficult catch for a Tennessee touchdown to tie the game at 45-45.

videos.headline: Vols fail to overcome Purdue in high-scoring thriller
videos.description: Despite getting off to a hot start, the Volunteers fall short in an offensive-powered Music City Bowl, resulting in a 48-45 overtime loss.
